WEBVTT

00:09:59.376 --> 00:10:02.182
In fact, they don't correlate
very much with IQ at all.

00:10:02.638 --> 00:10:04.288
They're about how you feel.

00:10:04.849 --> 00:10:08.872
There's a quote that I keep
coming back to, by Saint-ExupÃ©ry.

00:10:08.896 --> 00:10:10.837
He's the author of "The Little Prince."

00:10:10.861 --> 00:10:13.630
He said, "If you want to build a ship,

00:10:14.234 --> 00:10:18.855
don't drum up your men
to collect wood and give orders

00:10:18.879 --> 00:10:20.299
and distribute the work.

00:10:20.669 --> 00:10:25.236
Instead, teach them to yearn
for the vast and endless sea."

00:10:26.252 --> 00:10:28.398
In other words, I claim,

00:10:28.850 --> 00:10:32.010
if we really want to improve
our judgment as individuals